    <description>This agent acts as the digital front door for Onco Global patients, designed to deflect routine inquiries and streamline scheduling. It manages the full appointment lifecycle—booking, modifying, and canceling—across our 10+ hospitals. It helps patients navigate our oncology departments, discover the right specialists, and find facility information. By automating these interactions, it reduces wait times and allows our contact center to focus on complex cases. The agent interacts with empathy, prioritizing patient well-being while adhering to strict healthcare data guidelines within Health Cloud.</description>
